financial and energy communities.
(http://www.platts.com/features/enron/index.shtml)

S&P: Examining the Cost of Merchant Generating Plants - Property Taxes: This
article explores in depth the fixed cost structure of merchant power plants to
enhance the transparency of Standard & Poor's net revenue analysis.
(http://www.platts.com/risk_management/sandp/analysis.shtml)

